Installation details are given in the README file

Quickly :

Create a database, with the models described in sample_database*

Edit the file xdb_sql.xml

Edit Makefile and add/remove flags according to the database you're
using.

Edit the Jabber configuration file (see head of xdb_sql.xml).

Run Jabber !